                <p>HFFreelance is not just a store of ready-made websites,</p>
                <p>but a whole community of professional developers and clients,</p>
                <p>striving for success in the web space.</p>
                <p>We pride ourselves on our reputation as a reliable and quality provider of web developments</p>
                <p>and strive to make the process of creating</p>
                <p>and launching websites as simple and pleasant as possible for every client.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data">
            <div class="our-data">
                <div class="our-data-padding">
                    <h2 class="our-data-color">Our Email</h2>
                    <p></p>
                    <a href="mailto:hffreelancers@gmail.com" class="our-email"><h3 class="our-data-color">HFFreelancers@gmail.com</h3></a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="our-contact">
                <div class="our-contact-padding">
                    <h2 class="our-contact-color">Our Phone</h2>
                    <a href="tel:циферки" class="our-phone"><h3 class="our-contact-color">+7 123 456 78 90</h3></a>                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="services">
        <br>
        <br>
    </div>
