        <div class="services-container">
            <h2 style="color: #e7bc91; font-weight: 1000; margin-top: 70px;">Our services</h2>
            <div style="display: flex; margin-left: 100px; gap: 30px; margin-top: 20px;">
                <div style="word-break: break-word; max-width: 400px;">
                    <div class="service">
                        <h3 style="color: #f3d5b5">Website Design</h3>
                        <p>We create unique and creative designs that attract attention and enhance the user experience.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service">
                        <h3 style="color: #f3d5b5">Website Development</h3>
                        <p>We develop modern, responsive, and functional websites using the latest technologies.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service">
                        <h3 style="color: #f3d5b5">E-commerce</h3>
                        <p>We create effective online stores, helping your business grow and attract new customers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="word-break: break-word; width: 400px;">
                    <div class="service">
                        <h3 style="color: #f3d5b5">Custom Web Applications</h3>
                        <p>We develop custom web applications to meet your unique needs and goals.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service">
                        <h3 style="color: #f3d5b5">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h3>
                        <p>We optimize your website for search engines to increase its visibility and attract more traffic.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service">
                        <h3 style="color: #f3d5b5">Script Writing</h3>
                        <p>We create high-quality and reliable scripts for your website, enhancing its functionality and performance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="position: relative; left: 80%; top: -260px;">
                <img src="/images/terms.png" style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
                <br>
                <button class="order-btn" onclick="moreDetails()">Learn More</button>
