        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="reviews">
        <br>
        <br>
    </div>
    <h1 class="reviews-gradient">Customer reviews</h1>
    <p class="info-text">
        Check out the many positive reviews from our satisfied clients who share their experiences with us.
        We are proud of the quality of our work and always strive to improve our service.
    </p>
    <button id="moreReviews" class="moreReviews" onclick="allReviewsJoin()">Go to reviews</button>
